Definition: an inclination or desire
Example: used in the plural in the phrase `left to your own devices'; eventually the family left the house to the devices of this malevolent force; the children were left to their own devices
Synonyms: inclination, an, or, desire, used, in, the, plural, phrase, left, to, your, own, eventually, family, house, of, this, malevolent, force, children, were, their
Category: noun.cognition
